<!DOCTYPE html>


<html data-theme="light" lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Slide 12 - Ejercicio</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .slide-container {
            width: 1024px;
            height: 768px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        .font-poppins {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .text-corporate-blue {
            color: #114a90;
        }
        .bg-corporate-blue {
            background-color: #114a90;
        }
        .text-corporate-red {
            color: #C0504D;
        }
        .bg-corporate-red {
            background-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .border-corporate-red {
            border-color: #C0504D;
        }
        .border-corporate-blue {
            border-color: #114a90;
        }
        .step-card {
            position: relative;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .connector-line {
            position: absolute;
            left: 2rem;
            top: 100%;
            height: 2rem;
            width: 2px;
            background-color: #e5e7eb;
            z-index: 0;
        }
        .timer-circle {
            transform: rotate(-90deg);
            transform-origin: 50% 50%;
        }
        .timer-path-bg {
            stroke: #e5e7eb;
            stroke-width: 8;
            fill: none;
        }
        .timer-path-progress {
            stroke: #C0504D;
            stroke-width: 8;
            fill: none;
            stroke-dasharray: 283;
            stroke-dashoffset: 70;
            stroke-linecap: round;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="slide-container font-poppins">
<header class="w-full h-24 flex items-end justify-between px-12 pb-4 relative z-10" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 96px;">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-2 bg-corporate-red"></div>
<div class="flex flex-col">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
<span class="w-8 h-1 bg-corporate-red"></span>
<p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Ejercicio Práctico</p>
</div>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-corporate-blue">Tu turno: Define tus pilares</h2>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col items-end">
<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200">12</p>
</div>
</header>
<main class="flex-1 px-12 py-8 flex gap-12 items-center" style="position: absolute; top: 96px; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 672px;">
<div class="w-2/3 flex flex-col gap-6" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; top: 32px; left: 48px; width: 600px;">
<div class="step-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm flex items-start gap-6 relative z-10">
<div class="connector-line"></div>
<div class="w-16 h-16 flex-shrink-0 bg-red-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-red text-2xl border-4 border-white shadow-sm z-10">
<i class="fa-solid fa-users-viewfinder"></i>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 pt-1">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
<span class="bg-corporate-red text-white text-xs font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">Paso 1</span>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-700">Analiza a tu Audiencia</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-snug">¿Qué problemas, dudas o necesidades tiene tu cliente ideal?</p>
<div class="mt-2 bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded text-xs text-gray-400 italic border-l-2 border-gray-300">
<p>Ej: "No saben qué pedir", "Buscan ofertas", "Quieren ver la cocina"</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="step-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm flex items-start gap-6 relative z-10">
<div class="connector-line"></div>
<div class="w-16 h-16 flex-shrink-0 bg-blue-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-blue text-2xl border-4 border-white shadow-sm z-10">
<i class="fa-solid fa-bullhorn"></i>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 pt-1">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
<span class="bg-corporate-blue text-white text-xs font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">Paso 2</span>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-700">Define tu Mensaje</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-gray-600 text-lg leading-snug">¿Qué quieres que sepan sobre tu negocio? ¿Cuál es tu valor?</p>
<div class="mt-2 bg-gray-50 p-2 rounded text-xs text-gray-400 italic border-l-2 border-gray-300">
<p>Ej: "Usamos ingredientes frescos", "Somos expertos", "Ambiente familiar"</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="step-card bg-white border-l-4 border-corporate-blue rounded-r-xl p-6 shadow-md flex items-start gap-6 relative z-10">
<div class="w-16 h-16 flex-shrink-0 bg-gray-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-2xl border-4 border-white shadow-sm z-10">
<i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 pt-1">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-2">
<span class="bg-gray-800 text-white text-xs font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded uppercase">Resultado</span>
<h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-gray-800">Crea tus Pilares</h3>
</div>
<p class="text-gray-600 text-lg font-medium leading-snug">Combina ambos puntos y define de 3 a 5 temas principales.</p>
<div class="mt-3 flex gap-2">
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Pilar 1</span>
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Pilar 2</span>
<span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Pilar 3</span>
<span class="px-3 py-1 border border-dashed border-gray-300 text-gray-400 rounded-full text-xs">+</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="w-1/3 h-full flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 p-8 relative overflow-hidden" data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; top: 32px; left: 670px; width: 306px; height: 600px;">
<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-32 h-32 bg-corporate-red opacity-5 rounded-bl-full"></div>
<div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-32 h-32 bg-corporate-blue opacity-5 rounded-tr-full"></div>
<div class="relative w-48 h-48 mb-8">
<svg class="w-full h-full timer-circle" viewbox="0 0 100 100">
<circle class="timer-path-bg" cx="50" cy="50" r="45"></circle>
<circle class="timer-path-progress" cx="50" cy="50" r="45"></circle>
</svg>
<div class="absolute inset-0 flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
<span class="text-5xl font-bold text-gray-700">5</span>
<span class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-gray-500 font-semibold mt-1">Minutos</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="text-center">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-corporate-blue mb-2">¡Manos a la obra!</h3>
<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mb-6 px-4">
                        No lo pienses demasiado. Escribe lo primero que te venga a la mente basado en tu experiencia diaria.
                    </p>
<div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 text-corporate-red font-semibold text-sm">
<i class="fa-solid fa-pen-to-square"></i>
<span>Actividad Individual</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</main>
</div>

    <div style="position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; z-index: 9999; display: flex; gap: 10px; font-family: sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <a href="/slide-12" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Anterior</a>
        <span style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #fff; color: #333; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc;">13 / 26</span>
        <a href="/slide-14" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Siguiente</a>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>


